<div class="containter">
  <div class="app-card-container">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>A Little Bit About Myself</h1>
      
      <hr>
      
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width:250, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img'%>
          <div class="skills">
            <% @skills.each do |skill|%>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%=skill.title%></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-success"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%=skill.percent_utilized%>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%=skill.percent_utilized%>%"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <%end%>
          </div>
          <p class="lead card-block">
           <%= link_to "Hire Me", new_contact_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary hire-button"%>
          </p>
        </div>
          
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p>Innovative catalyst, with a wide range of functional expertise in Information Technology: programming languages, framework, databases, and platforms.  A quality-focused, technology professional with over five yearsâ€™ experience in web development with Drupal, and two year experience with Ruby on Rails.  Excels equally working autonomously or as part of a team.  Versatile and flexible with the ability to thrive in high-pressure situations.  Proactively navigates intense workloads.  Demonstrated business acumen and ability to meet fiscal and deadline commitments.  </p>
          <p>
            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary resume" 
              type='button'
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#jobHistory"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controler="jobHistory"
            >
              Job History
            </button>
            
            <button 
              class="btn btn-primary" 
              type='button'
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#education"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controler="education"
            >
              Education
            </button>
          </p>
          <br>
          <br>
          <p>
            <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 1
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 2
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 3
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="collapse" id="education">
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 1
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 2
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 3
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>